data.description: ADDITIONAL ACREAGE ADDED! This seller is highly motivated, bring us an offer. The adjoining 2.1 +/- acre parcel was previously listed for $76,000. The home with 4.5 +/- acres is now being offered for $515,000. With top of the line technology included in the purchase such as Starlink high-speed internet, a commercial grade multi-carrier cell signal booster, and a SimpliSafe Security System, this property not only offers one of the largest lots currently available in Glacier View Meadows, it also provides some of the best electronic packages for rural mountain living. Welcome to Hilltop Home and Views located in the Glacier View Meadows subdivision in Livermore, Colorado. Built in 2019, this home can be utilized as a primary residence for a family wanting to live a mountain lifestyle or for someone looking for a weekend getaway. This beautiful property sits on 4.5 +/- acres with some of the best view in all of Glacier View Meadows. (*Assumable VA loan at 2.25% for eligible veteran) Built on a naturally sloping 4.5 +/-acre lot, this unique home offers amazing views of the mountains. The minimal trees in the area allow miles of visibility and plenty of opportunity to spot wild life. Sitting on the highest point of the lot is the well built 1620 sq. ft. home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. With plenty of windows, picture perfect mountain views are present from all sides of the home. The open floor plan offers convenience from the dining room to the large kitchen completed with high end appliances. The spacious master bedroom offers 2 closets along with an attached bathroom featuring an oversized shower, bath tub, and 2 sinks.  Down the hallway from the master is the 2 spare bedrooms along with the laundry room where you can find a door that leads you to the back patio. From the dining room, step out on to the covered porch for easy access to the front portion of the property. Buyers agent to verify HOA and Taxes.
